dsDescriptionValue.value:
This repository contains the transition scores, attention scores, hidden states, sequences, and beam indices tensors belonging to EMTeC, the Eye Movements on Machine-Generated Texts Corpus. 

The eye-tracking data files including extensive documentation and all code used for the generation of the stimuli and the pre-processing of the data, as well as instructions on how to automatically download both the eye-tracking data files as well as the tensors, can be found in the GitHub repository https://github.com/DiLi-Lab/EMTeC.

datasetVersion.citation: Bolliger, Lena Sophia, 2024, "EMTeC Tensors", https://doi.org/10.7910/DVN/GCU0W8, Harvard Dataverse, V1
